race.comment: MAYBE NEXT WEEK (2) impressed when clocking a superb 22.71 over 401m at this track three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Has the ability and looks hard to top. SHE'S INTENSE (7) has been racing well lately, making it two on end when saluting at this track last time over 401m in (23.01). Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. In top form and looks a key chance again. SUMMER DREAM (6) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with five wins and a placing from seven tries. Scored by 4 lengths last time (22.54) in a Grade 3/4 over 401m at this track. Suited here and expected to run well. HUDSON (4) form at this distance reads well.
